        "text_7hwJgV": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For over seventy years, restaurants across the world have been serving food on Robert Gordon wares. Ask any chef and they will tell you that food looks better on a Robert Gordon plate. High quality, top design and the ability to custom create means that we are the best in the business.<br/><br/><br/>For 12 years Robert Gordon Australia have been partnering with Cedar Hospitality, inspiring, servicing and collaborating with the Hospitality  Industry to provide innovative and world-class collections. It is with great pride that we celebrate this milestone as we look to the future with enthusiasm and a commitment to our local Hospitality Industry.<br/><br/>The success of this longstanding partnership has been grounded in common values, in our uncompromising approach to Quality, Design, Innovation, Customer Service and an unparalleled knowledge of the Commercial Food Service industry.<br/><br/></p>",
            "text_size": "text-base",
            "text_line_limit": "none",
            "button_style": "btn--underline",
            "button_icon": "none"
          }
        }
